[30;1m27 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m28 | [0m[35mclass PerformanceBias(SingleDatasetCheck):[0m
[30;1m29 | [0m[35m    """[0m
[30;1m30 | [0m[35m    Check for performance differences between subgroups of a feature, optionally accounting for a co[0m
[30;1m31 | [0m[35m[0m
